item.title: SQL instead of Catherine Wheel
item.description: (transcribed from Book Six 11:08pm JST Saturday 27 June 2009 (day 14339)) 2:35 AM Tuesday 30 November 1993 Day 67 "Today" I did SQL stuff & looked for Cathy at SPB but I didn't find her. SPB sponsored Catherine Wheel in concert in the Houston Room. i was security, but only 30 or so people came so I cruised to work on SQL. I came back at the end of cleanup and helped take down the equipment.
